🚨Giveaway🚨-Closed
 
Things are warming up for summer! I’m celebrating by teaming up w/ @Woodward & @TheSkateparkProject to give away 10 scholarships for @Woodward Camp the same week I’m going! Good luck & can’t wait to meet you guys soon. See rules below. 🤗🍀
 
	•Let me know your favorite place to skate and tag who you want to go with.
	•I’ll choose 5 random comments for a total of 10 scholarships. 2 scholarships per comment chosen. 
	•Scholarship includes: Tuition, Room, Board
	•Scholarship does not include travel or incidentals 
	•Scholarship is valid on Lizzie Weeks at camp (Week 8 at West, Week 11 at PA) 
	•Scholarship is valid for entrants ages 7-17. Nobody outside of this age range is permitted to attend camp as a camper.

❗️Comment entry deadline is June 3 11:59 pm.❗️

…Director’s note: Humanity Stoked is about 9 key issues that affect all of humanity, and this planet that we all share. It’s not really about skateboarding, so it was nice to drop this clip from the female empowerment part of the film when we actually do talk about it for a bit. Thanks @lizziearmento for wanting to set a great example, and be someone young girls can look up to. So much love, respect, and gratitude!
